headline: Rockwell Automation to Host Annual Investor Meeting
summary: MILWAUKEE, October 01, 2025--Rockwell Automation, Inc. (NYSE: ROK) will host its annual investor meeting on Wednesday, Nov. 19, in conjunction with the company’s Automation Fair® being held at McCormick Place in Chicago, Illinois.
